
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-francois-rtgwg-segment-routing-uloop-01.txt'>
    <title>"Loop avoidance using Segment Routing", Pierre Francois, Clarence Filsfils, Ahmed Bashandy, Stephane Litkowski</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-francois-rtgwg-segment-routing-uloop-01.txt</link>
    <description>This document presents a mechanism aimed at providing loop avoidance in the case of IGP network convergence event.  The solution relies on the temporary use of SR policies ensuring loop-freeness over the post-convergence paths from the converging node to the destination.</description>
    <dc:date>2016-12-14T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
